quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  6,28,haan yeh jo kuch pehlay chupaya karte they ( aaj ) un par zahir hogaya hai aur agar yeh ( duniya mein ) lout’tay bhi jayen to jin ( kamon ) se un ko manakiya gaya tha wohi phir karne lagen. kuch shak nahi ke yeh jhutay hain
  6,29,aur kehte hain ke hamari jo duniya ki zindagi hai bas yahi ( zindagi ) hai aur hum ( marnay ke baad ) phir zindah nahi kiye jayen ge
  6,30,aur kash tum ( un ko is waqt ) dekho jab yeh apne perwar-digaar ke samnay kharray kiye jayen ge aur woh farmaiye gakiya yeh ( dobarah zindah hona ) barhaq nahi to kahin ge kyun nahi perwar-digaar ki qasam ( bilkul barhaq hai ) khuda farmaiye ga ab kufar ke badlay ( jo duniya mein karte they ) azaab ( ke mazay ) chako
  6,31,jin logon ne khuda ke rubaroo haazir honay ko jhoot samgha woh ghatay mein aagaye. yahan taq ke jab un par qayamat nagahan آموجود hogi to bol utheen ge ke ( haae ) is taqseer par afsos hai jo hum ne qayamat ke baray mein ki. aur woh apne ( aamaal ke ) boojh apni pithon par uthaye hue hon ge. dekho jo boojh yeh utha rahay hain bohat bura hai
  6,32,aur duniya ki zindagi to aik khail aur mashgolah hai. aur bohat acha ghar to akhirat ka ghar hai ( yani ) un ke liye jo ( khuda se ) drtay hain.kiya tum samajte nahi
  6,33,hum ko maloom hai ke un ( kafiroon ) ki baatein tumhe ranj pohanchati hain ( magar ) yeh tumhari takzieeb nahi karte balkay zalim khuda ki ayaton se inkaar karte hain
  6,34,aur tum se pehlay kabhi paighambar jhutlaye jatay rahay to woh takzieeb aur aeza par sabr karte rahay yahan taq ke un ke paas hamari madad pahunchti rahi aur khuda ki baton ko koi bhi badalny wala nahi. aur tum ko payghambaroon ( ke ahwaal ) ki khabrain poanch chuki hain ( to tum bhi sabr se kaam lau )
  6,35,aur agar un ki rogrdani tum par shaq guzarti hai to agar taaqat ho to zameen mein koi surang dhoond nikalu ya aasman mein seerhi ( talaash karo ) phir un ke paas koi moujza lao. aur agar khuda chahta to sab ko hadaayat par jama kardaita pas tum hargiz نادانوں mein nah hona
